# Company Tools Suite

Collection of tools for partner and relationship management.

## 🎯 Available Tools

### 1. **RM Incentive Calculator**
Real-time incentive calculations for Relationship Managers
- **Type**: Standalone Tool
- **Access**: [View Locally](./RM_Incentive_Calculator%20(1).html)

---

### 2. **VRM Partner Mapping Engine**
Intelligent VRM and partner data management automation
- **Type**: Web Application (Live)
- **Status**: 🟢 Production
- **Access**: [Open Live App →](./vrm-partner-mapping/)
- **Direct Link**: [vrmauto.lovable.app](https://vrmauto.lovable.app)
- **Built with**: Lovable, React, TypeScript

